<paragraph blockId="43.[151,1436,507,1110]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,300,831,858]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Habitat:</emphasis>
Grama-needlegrass-wheatgrass grassland vegetation 
<typeStatus box="[915,967,832,858]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">type</typeStatus>
. Short- to mid-grassland, rangeland (see 
<bibRefCitation author="Dennis, D. S. &amp; Lavigne, R. J." box="[151,438,867,894]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" pagination="48 - 62" refId="ref102141" refString="Dennis, D. S. &amp; Lavigne, R. J. (1976 a) Ethology of Efferia varipes with comments on species coexistence (Diptera: Asilidae). Journal of the Kansas Entomological Society, 49, 48 - 62." type="journal article" year="1976">Dennis &amp; Lavigne 1976a</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="43.[151,1436,507,1110]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,316,904,930]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Ethology:</emphasis>
Forages from both the ground and vegetation depending on the temperature of the ground surface (see 
<bibRefCitation author="Dennis, D. S. &amp; Lavigne, R. J." box="[203,485,939,966]" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" pagination="48 - 62" refId="ref102141" refString="Dennis, D. S. &amp; Lavigne, R. J. (1976 a) Ethology of Efferia varipes with comments on species coexistence (Diptera: Asilidae). Journal of the Kansas Entomological Society, 49, 48 - 62." type="journal article" year="1976">Dennis &amp; Lavigne 1976a</bibRefCitation>
as 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Williston" baseAuthorityYear="1885" box="[523,690,940,966]" class="Insecta" family="Asilidae" genus="Efferia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="43" pageNumber="44" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="varipes">
<emphasis box="[523,690,940,966]" italics="true" pageId="43" pageNumber="44">Efferia varipes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
